          <h4 class="partner_h">Raincross Medical Group</h4>
          <p>At Inland Empire Weight Loss, we have worked closely with all of the physicians at Raincross Medical Group. Obesity is a common problem among people with medical conditions such as Diabetes, Hypertension, and Obstructive Sleep apnea. Inland Empire Weight Loss is proud to work with the physicians at Raincross Medical Group to provide services in Bariatric Medicine to help with weight loss and weight related medical problems.</p>
          <a class="partner_a" href="http://www.raincrossmedicalgroup.net/knopke.html" title="visit Raincross Medical Group" target="_blank">www.raincrossmedicalgroup.net/knopke</a>
     </div>
