          <h4 class="partner_h">Imagine Plastic Surgery</h4>
          <p>Imagine Plastic Surgery and Inland Empire Weight Loss have worked closely together since 2008.  Some of our weight loss patients who lose a significant amount of weight will develop excess skin on their arms, face, and abdomen.  Through our relationship with Imagine Plastic Surgery, we are able to arrange for surgical correction of these problems when they are confronted.</p>
